  "description": "<p>A lightweight winter bag for ski tourers, alpine climbers and winter mountaineers. Premium 800 fill-power down offers grandiose loft, but takes up only modest space when compressed into a stuff sack. The recycled nylon shell fabric is water resistant so it sheds snowmelt and condensation and won't wick moisture off the wet walls of the tent.</p><ul><li>Recycled nylon shell with a PFC-free DWR finish</li><li>Lined with soft, woven recycled nylon</li><li>800 fill-power goose down meets the Responsible Down Standard</li><li>Zipper ends just above the footbox for access and venting without excess weight</li><li>Lightweight #5 YKK zipper</li><li>Draft tube and neck yoke block heat loss via the zipper</li><li>Small zippered interior pocket lets you keep contact lenses from freezing</li><li>Hanging loops at foot for storing or drying</li><li>Includes a water resistant stuff sack and home storage cube</li></ul>",
